glish": "In the Name of Allah, the most Gracious, the most Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "(Shuru karta hu) Allah ke naam se Jo bada maher-baan nehaayat rahem karne waala hai.", "Urdu": "اللہ کے نام سے (شروع کرتا ہوں) جو بڑا مہربا ن نہایت رحم کرنے والا ہے۔", "RArabic": "BISMILLAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1017591, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "By the truth of Yaseen (a title of the Holy Prophet) and the Quran full of wisdom And for the sake of Taa-haa (another title of the Holy Prophet) and the great Quran. O He Who is able to fulfill the desires of those ask. O He Who knows what is in the heart. O He Who banishes sorrow from the sorrowful. O He Who dispels grief from those who grieve. O He Who is merciful to old men. O He Who provides for infants. O He Who needs not to be explained. Send blessings upon Muhammad and his progeny and fulfill for me.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Waasta deta hu Yaasin aur Quraan'e hakeem ka aur waasta deta hu Taha o Quraan'e Azeem ka, ay Woh jo sawaal karne waalo’n ki haajato’n par qaadir hai, ay Woh keh dilo’n ki baate’n jaanta hai aur dukhyaaro’n ke dukh dur karta hai, aur gham-zado’n ke gham mitaata hai, ay boodho’n par rahem karne waale, ay chhote bachcho’n ko rozi dene waale, ay woh jise sharah o bayaan ki zaroorat nahi, rehmat naazil farma sarkaar'e Muhammad (s.a.w.a) aur Aale Muhammad (a.s) par aur meri yeh aur yeh haajaat poori farma.", "Urdu": "واسطہ دیتا ہو ں یٰسین اور قرآن حکیم کا اور واسطہ دیتا ہوں طہٰ و قرآن عظیم کا اے وہ جو سوال کرنے والوں کی حاجتوں پر قادر ہے اے وہ کہ دلوں کی باتیں جانتاہے اور دکھیاروں کے دکھ دور کرتا ہے اورغم زدوں کے غم مٹاتا ہے اے بوڑ ھوں پر رحم کرنے والے اے چھوٹے بچوں کوروزی دینے والے اے وہ جسے شرح وبیان کی ضرورت نہیں رحمت فرما سر کار محمدؐ و آلؑ محمدؐ پر اور میری یہ اور یہ حاجات پوری فرما۔", "RArabic": "BE-HAQQE YAASIN WAL-QUR-AA-NIL HAKEEME, WA BE-HAQQE TAA-HAA WAL-QUR-AA-NIL A’ZEEME, YAA MAIY-YAQ-DERO A’LAA HAWAA'e JIS SAA'e LEENA, YAA MAIY-YA’LAMO MAA FIZ-ZAMEE-RE YAA MO-NAFFE-SAN A’NIL MAKROO-BEENA YAA MO-FARRE-JAN A’NIL MAGH-MOO-MEENA, YAA RAAHE-MASH SHAIY-KHIL KABEERE, YAA RAAZE-QAT TIF-LIS SAGHEE-RE YAA MAN LAA YAH-TAAJO ILAT TAF-SEERE SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIW WA AALE MOHAMMADIN WAF-A’L-BEE.", "ArabicText1": "بِحَقِّ يٰس وَالْقُرْآنِ الْحَكِيْمِ وَبِحَقِّ طٰهٰ وَالْقُرْآنِ الْعَظِيْمِ يَا مَنْ يَّقْدِرُ عَلٰى حَوَائِجِ السَّائِلِيْنَ يَا مَنْ يَّعْلَمُ مَا فِي الضَّمِيْرِ يَا مُنَفِّسًا عَنِ الْمَكْرُوْبِيْنَ يَا مُفَرِّجًا عَنِ الْمَغْمُوْمِيْنَ يَا رَاحِمَ الشَّيْخِ الْكَبِيْرِ يَا رَازِقَ الطِّفْلِ الصَّغِيْرِ يَا مَنْ لَّا يَحْتَاجُ اِلَى التَّفْسِيْرِ صَلِّ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَافْعَلْ بِيْ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": 